Package: gghighcharts
Title: Convert ggplot2 Plots to Highcharts Widgets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Zhenya", "Kosovan", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "yevhen.kosovan@outlook.com")
Description: Translates a restricted subset of ggplot2 plots into interactive
    highcharter widgets. Works by inspecting the built plot (via ggplot_build())
    rather than parsing user source code. Supports line, scatter, and bar/column
    charts with numeric, discrete, and date axes.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 3.4.0),
    highcharter (>= 0.9.4),
    htmlwidgets,
    rlang,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
